</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="14" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[831,1436,513,602]" pageId="3" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[831,935,514,537]" pageId="3" pageNumber="14">Remarks</emphasis>
: Males are unknown. The second specimen known is a female from Northern Nigeria, Ropp Hills, 20.VII.1920, and has no abdomen.
</paragraph>
